INSERT INTO `content_type_custom_vehicle` VALUES (3689,3689,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Hybrid, 40 MPG, Sporty</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2011 Hyundai Sonata Hybrid is a sporty looking sedan that gets Excellent fuel economy, has a comfortable and handsome cabin and a smooth ride.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard equipment on the Sonata includes 16-inch alloy wheels, keyless ignition/entry, dual-zone automatic climate control, cruise control, full power accessories, heated and folding outside mirrors, automatic headlights, a tilt-and-telescoping steering column, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, an eight-way power driver seat, a trip computer, Bluetooth and a six-speaker audio system with CD player, satellite radio, an iPod adapter and an auxiliary audio jack.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2011 Hyundai Sonata Hybrid is powered by a 2.4-liter four-cylinder gasoline engine generating 166 horsepower and 154 pound-feet of torque, paired with an electric motor making 40 hp and 151 lb-ft. Combined, the two power units are good for 206 peak hp and 193 lb-ft of torque. A six-speed automatic with manual shift control is the only available transmission. The EPA estimates Sonata Hybrid fuel economy at 36 mpg city/40 mpg highway and 38 combined.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Safety features on the 2011 Hyundai Sonata Hybrid include antilock brakes, traction control, stability control, front side-impact airbags, full-length side curtain airbags and active front head restraints.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2011','Hyundai','Sonata Hybrid','12995.00','141599','4 Door','Silver','Gray Cloth','2.4L 4 Cylinder','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','Front Wheel Drive','Gasoline Hybrid','AM/FM CD','4','11SONATAHYBRID5163','KMHEC4A49BA005163'),(3538,3538,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>AWD, 2.0L Turbo Charged Engine, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** The 2008 Audi A4 2.0T Quattro AWD with **Power Sunroof** is a fine choice thanks to its reasonable price, high-quality interior and engaging personality. The A4 offers Premium cabin design and materials, communicative chassis makes it rewarding to drive, and All Wheel Drive versatility.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The A4 2.0T sedan comes standard with Heated Leather, power seats, a sunroof, dual-zone automatic climate control and a 10-speaker, six-CD/MP3 changer.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the A4 is a 2.0-liter turbocharged inline-4 produces 200 hp and 207 pound-feet of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 19 MPG City and 27 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard safety features include antilock brakes, traction control, stability control, front-seat side airbags and full-length side curtain airbags.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','Audi','A4 2.0T Quattro AWD','12995.00','111418','4 Door','Black','Gray Leather','2.0L 4 Cylinder Turbo','6 Speed Automatic','AWD','Gas','AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','08A4QUATTRO8785','WAUDF78E68A168785'),(1597,1597,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Convertible, Heated Leather, V6, Sharp</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Nissan\'s crown jewel. For the money, the 2004 Nissan 350Z Roadster Convertible is one of the best performance buys on the market. The 350Z boasts a smooth and powerful V6 engine, excellent handling, available drop-top version, a bargain compared to anything that can run with it.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This 350Z is equipped with Black Heated Leather Interior, Power Seats, Power Fold Down Top, Bose Sound System, Auto Transmission, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the 350Z is a 3.5L V6 Engine that gets Fuel Economy of 16 MPG City and 23 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. &nbsp;Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2004','Nissan','350Z Roadster Touring Convertible Coupe','14900.00','107150','Convertible','Gray','Black','3.5L V6','Automatic','2 Wheel Drive Rear','Gas','Bose AM/FM CD Tape','2','D04 NISSAN 350Z GRAY','JN1AZ36A54T002331'),(3842,3842,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, Diesel, Long Bed, Heated Leather, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** **TURBO DIESEL** **LONG BED** **HEATED LEATHER** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>With this year\'s increase in output for the PowerStroke Turbodiesel V8, robust new chassis and numerous refinements to the cabin, the 2008 Ford F-350 Super Duty Lariat Super Cab 4x4 Long Bed is back in competitive form in the 1-ton pickup class.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Ford F-350 Super Duty one-ton pickup has been redesigned for 2008. Under the skin, a number of major upgrades take place. Ford says the chassis is stronger than before and now has a new type of coating for improved corrosion resistance. The rear suspension has also been tweaked to improve ride and handling without compromising capability. The PowerStroke diesel engine grows from 6.0 to 6.4 liters and now makes an impressive 350 horsepower and 650 pound-feet of torque. Also new this year are higher-grade cabin materials, a standard MP3 audio jack, and available power telescoping/folding side mirrors.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>behind that grille is a larger PowerStroke diesel engine. It\'s now at 6.4 liters, versus 6.0 liters last year, and features twin turbochargers a small one for quick response off the line and a larger one that kicks in to beef up the midrange and common-rail fuel injection with high-tech injectors. Because these injectors administer fuel in up to five metered spurts per combustion cycle rather than all at once, reliability is improved, emissions are reduced and the engine even runs quieter. Another benefit is quick startup this diesel can fire up in under 2 seconds at minus-20 degrees.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This F350 is also equipped with Factory Brake Control, Rear Power Sliding Window, Power Seats, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','Ford','F350 Super Duty Lariat Super Cab 4x4 Long Bed Diesel','22900.00','152684','Pickup','Black','Tan Leather','6.4L Power Stroke Turbo Diesel','5 Speed Automatic','4x4','Diesel','AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','08F350DIESEL7616','1FTWX31R58EC07616'),(3492,3492,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>74K Miles, DVD, Navigation, Power Sunroof, Heated Leather, Back Up Camera, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**74K MILES** **DVD** **NAVIGATION** **BACK UP CAMERA**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This 2008 Chevy Suburban LTZ 4x4 is a compelling choice if you have a large family looking for a full sized SUV that\'s loaded up. The Suburban offers class-leading cargo capacity, attractive interior, comfortable seating and ride, and a smooth V8.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Suburban is equipped with Heated Leather Seats, Power Sunroof, Driver Memory, Adjustable Pedals, Rear Air/Heat, Rear Power Lift Gate, Traction Control, Power Options and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Suburban is a 5.3-liter V8 with 320 horsepower and 340 pound-feet of torque. Equipped with GM\'s cylinder deactivation technology, this V8 promises better than normal fuel efficiency to the tune of 14 city and 19 highway for 2008.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Four-wheel antilock disc brakes are standard on all Suburbans, as are stability control and GM\'s OnStar emergency communications system. A three-row side curtain airbag system with a rollover sensor is standard on all Suburbans. In government crash tests, the 2008 Chevy Suburban was awarded a top five-star rating for protecting the driver and passenger in a frontal collision.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','Chevy','Suburban LTZ 4x4 with 3rd Row Seating','27900.00','74488','SUV','Black','Black Leather','5.3L V8','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Flex Fuel E-85','Bose AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','08SUBURBANLTZ0739','3GNFK16328G100739'),(3493,3493,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>New Tires, DVD, Navigation, Bucket Seats, Power Sunroof, Heated Leather, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**NEW TIRES** **DVD** **NAVIGATION** **BUCKET SEATS** **BACK UP CAMERA**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2007 GMC Yukon Denali AWD V8 continues as a leading choice for a traditional large SUV with **3rd Row Seating** thanks to its handsome styling, comfortable cabin and strong towing and hauling capabilities. The Yukon Denali offers High-quality fit and finish, a handsome cabin, comfortable ride, smooth powertrain, seats up to seven passengers.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Yukon Denali also features a unique grille and trim, 18-inch alloy wheels, running boards, adaptive suspension with rear load-leveling, heated and cooled seats, a power-adjustable and heated steering wheel, triple-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable pedals, rear power lift gate, remote vehicle starter, rear parking assist, universal home remote, a six-disc CD changer with premium Bose sound and \"Turn-by-Turn\" navigation for the OnStar system.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The GMC Yukon Denali features a 6.2-liter V8 that makes 403 hp and 417 lb-ft of torque, mated to a six-speed automatic transmission with tap-up/tap-down shifting. A properly equipped Yukon can tow from 8,200 to 8,500 pounds depending on model and engine specs. Fuel Economy is 12 MPG City and 18 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Antilock disc brakes, stability control, OnStar communications, front-seat side impact airbags and full-length head curtain airbags with rollover sensor are standard on all Yukons.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','GMC','Yukon Denali AWD V8 with 3rd Row Seating','21900.00','111029','SUV','Black','Black Leather','6.2L V8','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','AWD','Gas','Bose AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','07YUKONDENALI8968','1GKFK63827J338968'),(3788,3788,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Crew Cab Room, 4.8L V8, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2006 GMC Sierra 1500 SLE Crew Cab 4x4 Short Bed is a solid truck in terms of its drivetrain, roomy interior and unique features.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Sierra is equipped with Cloth Interior, Shift on the Floor 4x4, Power Options, and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Sierra is a 4.8L V8 Engine that gets Fuel Economy of 13 MPG City and 17 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2006','GMC','Sierra 1500 SLE Crew Cab 4x4 Short Bed','14900.00','136024','Pickup','Blue','Gray Cloth','4.8L V8','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','06SIERRA1500SLE8484','2GTEK13V561308484'),(3789,3789,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Heated Leather, Panoramic Sunroof, V6, AWD</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Strong acceleration, agile handling, a smooth ride and a roomy passenger compartment give the 2008 Ford Edge Limited AWD major points in the midsize crossover segment. The Edge features a Quiet and comfortable ride, agile handling, potent V6, all major safety features are standard, and a roomy cabin.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Edge is equipped with Vista Roof which consists of a power front sunroof and fixed rear skylight, Traction Control, a chrome beltline body accent, heated exterior mirrors, leather upholstery, heated front seats, dual-zone automatic climate control, Power Options, driver-seat memory, a power passenger seat that folds flat and Microsoft Sync.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Edge comes with a 3.5-liter V6 rated for 265 hp and 250 pound-feet of torque. A six-speed automatic transmission is standard. Fuel Economy clocks in at 15 MPG City and 22 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Antilock disc brakes, stability control with rollover avoidance logic, front-seat side airbags and full-length side curtain airbags are all standard. In government crash tests, the 2008 Ford Edge nearly had a perfect sweep. It scored five stars out of five for the driver and four stars for the passenger in frontal-impact tests, while it earned five stars in side-impact testing for both front and rear passengers. In Insurance Institute for Highway Safety crash tests, it scored the highest possible rating of \"Good\" in both frontal-offset and side-impact testing.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','Ford','Edge Limited AWD','13900.00','112940','SUV','Burnt Orange','Tan Leather','3.5L V6','6 Speed Automatic','AWD','Gas','AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','08EDGELIMITED3150','2FMDK49C48BB13150'),(3682,3682,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>77K Miles, RWD, Sporty, 3.5L V6</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**77K MILES** If a big American sedan with big-time V8 thrust is your thing, the 2010 Dodge Charger SXT RWD is one of the best and last of this breed. The Charger features roomy interior, and agreeable ride and seats.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Charger is equipped with Cloth Interior, Power Drivers Seat and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Charger is powered by a 3.5-liter V6 good for 250 hp and 250 lb-ft of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 17 MPG City and 20 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2010','Dodge','Charger SXT 3.5L V6 RWD','12995.00','77932','4 Door','Black','Gray Cloth','3.5L High Output V6','4 Speed Automatic','2 Wheel Drive Rear','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','10CHARGERSXT6352','2B3CA3CV9AH286352'),(3509,3509,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, Bucket Seats, Navigation, Back Up Camera, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** **NAVIGATION** **BUCKET SEATS** **BACK UP CAMERA**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2008 GMC Yukon Denali AWD V8 is a solid choice for a large luxury SUV thanks to its handsome, comfortable cabin and strong towing ability.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The high-line Yukon Denali features a unique grille, 18-inch alloy wheels, an adaptive suspension with a rear load-leveling feature, a power liftgate, heated leather as well as heated second-row captain\'s chairs, a premium Bose sound system, 12-way power/heated front seats, power-folding mirrors with turn signals, and a 50/50-split third-row seat, Power Sunroof, and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The GMC Yukon Denali boasts a 6.2-liter V8 380 hp and 415 lb-ft matched to a six-speed automatic transmission with a manual-shift mode. Fuel Economy clocks in at 12 MPG City and 18 MPG Hwy. Properly equipped, a Yukon Denali can tow up to 7900 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Antilock disc brakes, stability control and full-length side curtain airbags with a rollover sensor are standard on all Yukons. Front-seat side airbags are not available. In National Highway Traffic Safety Administration frontal crash testing, the Yukon scored a perfect five stars for the driver and front passenger.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','GMC','Yukon Denali AWD V8 with 3rd Row Seating','22900.00','120084','SUV','Black','Black Leather','6.2L V8','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','AWD','Gas','Bose AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','08YUKONDENALI0363','1GKFK63808J130363'),(116,116,'<p><span style=\"color: #ff0000; font-size: large;\"><strong>500 Horsepower Mustang Shelby GT 500 with 6300 Miles </strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Here is a super sharp, clean and Sport Inspired Mustang GT 500 Shelby with 6 Speed Manual and Navigation.&nbsp; Returning once again for 2008, the Ford Shelby GT500, based on the popular Shelby GT, is sure to turn heads wherever it travels. Inspired by the Shelby big-block Mustang of the 1960s, the GT500, which is a joint collaboration between Mustang customizer Shelby and Ford\'s Special Vehicle Team SVT, truly is a performance-powered Mustang.&nbsp; There are many ways in which the GT500 stands apart from other Mustangs. For one, it boasts a supercharged 5.4-liter V8 engine capable of outputting an estimated 500 hp and 480 lb.-ft. of torque.&nbsp; comes with a MacPherson strut independent front suspension with Reverse-L lower control arms, backed by spring rates and an upgraded stabilizer for improved handling and stopping performance. Next, the GT500 is only available with a 6-speed manual transmission, designed exclusively for performance driving. In fact, the cars heavy-duty transmission is the same in design as the race-winning Mustang FR500C.&nbsp; As for braking, the GT500 boasts four-piston Brembo calipers, each fitted to 14-inch Brembo vented rotors up front. It also features 11.8-inch vented discs in the rear.&nbsp; </strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Very well equipped, this Mustang GT comes with Sport Alloy Rims, As for tread, its available with 18 x 9.5 inch wheels featuring 255/45ZR high-performance tires up front and 285/40ZR high-performance tires in back, Sport Trim, Black Leather Interior, Power Drivers Seat, Power Windows and Locks, Cruise, In Dash Navigation System, 6 Speed Shifter, Sirus Satellite Radio, Air and much more.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions.&nbsp; Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','Ford','Mustang Shelby GT 500 6 Speed Manual','42900.00','6300','2 Door','Gray','Black Leather','5.4L Super Charged','6 Speed Manual','2 Wheel Drive Rear','Gas','AM/FM CD','2','D08 Ford Mustang Shelby Gray','1ZVHT88SX85112640'),(3179,3179,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>5 Speed Manual, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2006 Volkswagen Jetta 2.5 Pkg 1 with **5 Speed Manual** offers a near ideal balance between ride and handling. This, along with its Great Fuel Economy, premium cabin materials and long features list, makes it a great choice for small-car buyers. The Jetta 2.5 boasts a comfortable ride, rich interior materials, loads of standard safety features, excellent crash test scores, and solid build quality.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Jetta is equipped with Heated Leather Interior, Power Sunroof, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Jetta is a 2.5-liter five-cylinder with 150 hp and 170 lb-ft of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 19 MPG City and 28 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Four-wheel antilock disc brakes, seat-mounted side airbags for front occupants and full-length head curtain airbags are standard across the line. In NHTSA crash testing, the VW Jetta received four stars for driver and passenger protection in frontal impacts, and five stars for front and rear seat protection in side impacts. The IIHS rated the VW Jetta \"Good\" its highest rating after conducting its offset frontal-impact crash test. The sedan also aced the side-impact test conducted by the IIHS.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2006','Volkswagen','Jetta 2.5L 5 Speed Manual','7900.00','101775','4 Door','Silver','Gray Leather','2.5L 5 Cylinder','5 Speed Manual','Front Wheel Drive','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','05JETTA3307','3VWSG71K66M713307'),(3775,3775,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>V6, Navigation, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**V6** **HEATED LEATHER** **NAVIGATION** **POWER SUNROOF**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2008 Honda Accord EX-L V6 maintains and improves upon the aspects that have made past Accords so great. Plus, the sedan and coupe\'s eye-catching styling proves that reliable transportation doesn\'t have to be bland. The Accord features a Powerful and fuel-efficient V6 engine, ample passenger space, balanced approach to handling and ride comfort, and striking styling.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Accord is equipped with Leather Interior, Power Seats, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Accord is a 3.5-liter V6 that produces 268 hp and 248 lb-ft of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 19 MPG City and 29 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>All Accords come standard with antilock disc brakes, stability and traction control, front side airbags and full-length curtain airbags.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if 