type of coating for improved corrosion resistance. The rear suspension has also been tweaked to improve ride and handling without compromising capability. The PowerStroke diesel engine grows from 6.0 to 6.4 liters and now makes an impressive 350 horsepower and 650 pound-feet of torque.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This F350 is equipped with Vinyl Interior, Manual Locks and Crank Windows, AC, Toneau Cover and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Available behind that grille is a larger PowerStroke diesel engine. It\'s now at 6.4 liters, versus 6.0 liters last year, and features twin turbochargers a small one for quick response off the line and a larger one that kicks in to beef up the midrange and common-rail fuel injection with high-tech injectors. Because these injectors administer fuel in up to five metered spurts per combustion cycle rather than all at once, reliability is improved, emissions are reduced and the engine even runs quieter. Another benefit is quick startup this diesel can fire up in under 2 seconds at minus-20 degrees.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','Ford','F350 XL Super Duty Super Cab 4x4 Long Bed Diesel','17900.00','141787','Pickup','Red','Gray Cloth','6.4L V8 Power Stroke Diesel','5 Speed Automatic','4x4','Diesel','AM/FM CD','4','08F350XLDIESEL1232','1FTWX31R68EA51232'),(3726,3726,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Quad Cab, 4x4, V8</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Still the king of big-truck attitude, the 2006 Dodge Ram 1500 SLT Quad Cab 4x4 Short Box can handle the diverse duties of comfortable daily driver and capable workhorse with equal ease. The Ram features Strong output from it\'s V8, sharp steering, and compliant ride.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Ram is equipped with alloy wheels, standard cruise control, cloth seating, keyless entry and power windows, locks and mirrors.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Ram is powered by a 4.7-liter V8 that carnks out 235 hp and 300 lb-ft of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 12 MPG City and 17 MPG Hwy. Properly equipped, a 4WD Ram Quad Cab can pull 8,600 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Sold','2006','Dodge','Ram 1500 SLT Quad Cab 4x4 Short Bed','12900.00','125868','Pickup','Black','Gray Cloth','4.7L V8','5 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','06RAM1500SLT9734','1D7HU18N76J229734'),(3010,3010,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, DVD, Navigation, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**One Owner** As one of GM\'s triplets in its full-size SUV family, the 2007 GMC Yukon XL Denali with **DVD Entertainment**, **Navigation**, **Back Up Camera** and **3rd Row Seats** bridges the gap between the somewhat plain Chevy Suburban and the over-the-top Cadillac Escalade ESV. The Yukon XL is essentially a longer version of the Yukon, with a 14-inch-longer wheelbase and an overall length that, at 222.4 inches, stretches some 20 inches longer than the Yukon. The 2007 GMC Yukon XL is completely redesigned and gets more of everything that\'s important in the large SUV segment power, cabin space, convenience features and safety equipment.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Denali features a unique grille, 18-inch alloy wheels, Navigation, XM satellite radio, heated seats including the second row, driver memory, adjustable pedals, traction control, rear power lift gate, a premium Bose sound system with a six-disc CD changer, rear air/heat, and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Denali is powered by a 6.2-liter V8 380 hp and 417 lb-ft mated to a six-speed automatic transmission with a manual-shift mode. Towing capacities for the standard Yukon XL is 7,100 pounds. Fuel Economy clocks in at 13 MPG City and 19 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Stability control dubbed StabiliTrak with a rollover sensor is standard, as are four-wheel antilock disc brakes, a tire-pressure monitoring system and the OnStar telematics system. Standard Denali head curtain airbags for all three rows.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','GMC','Yukon XL Denali AWD V8 with 3rd Row Seating','23495.00','109265','SUV','Black','Black Leather','6.2L V8','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','AWD','Gas','Bose AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','274097','1GKFK66897J274097'),(3353,3353,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Hybrid, DVD, Navigation, Back Up Camera, Heated Leather, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**DVD Entertainment** Combining 21-mpg fuel economy with the towing capacity of a traditional SUV, the 2009 GMC Yukon Hybrid 4x4 is an amazing piece of machinery. The Yukon Hybrid features Amazing fuel economy for a full-size SUV, handsome cabin with solid build quality, comfortable ride, and seats eight passengers.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Developed in concert by BMW and DaimlerChrysler and General Motors, the Yukon Hybrid\'s \"two-mode\" technology starts with a 6.0-liter V8 with cylinder-deactivation technology -- it essentially turns that V8 into a V4 when full power isn\'t needed. The V8 is coupled to a pair of 60-kilowatt motors packaged within the transmission for electric motivation. like other full hybrids, the Yukon Hybrid can be propelled up to around 25 mph solely under electric power, which is why its city fuel economy 21 mpg is virtually the same as its highway 22 mpg.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard equipment includes 18-inch alloy wheels, rear park assist with rearview camera, tinted windows, power-folding heated side mirrors and tri-zone automatic climate control. A trip computer, Bluetooth connectivity, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, remote ignition, leather upholstery, power front seats and a removable 50/50-split third-row seat are also standard. In-car entertainment includes a navigation system, a hybrid system display and a nine-speaker Bose audio system with a CD/MP3 player, an auxiliary audio jack and satellite radio with real-time traffic reporting.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Yukon is powered by a 6.0-liter V8 engine coupled to a pair of 60-kilowatt electric motors located inside what GM calls an electrically variable transmission. Together, they produce 332 horsepower and 367 pound-feet of torque.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2009','GMC','Yukon Hybrid 4x4 with 3rd Row Seating','21900.00','129906','SUV','Black','Black Leather','6.0L V8','4 Speed Shiftable Automatic','4x4','Gas','Bose AM/FM CD','4','09YUKONHYBRID6026','1GKFK13509R106026'),(3834,3834,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, Dual DVD, Navigation, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** **DUAL DVD IN HEADREST** **NAVIGATION** **HEATED LEATHER** **REAR POWER LIFT GATE** **POWER SUNROOF** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2007 Chevy Tahoe LT 4x4 is a compelling choice for any family looking for a fully loaded Full Sized SUV. The Tahoe boasts an attractive interior with solid materials, smooth ride quality, smooth V8, and comfortable seating.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Tahoe is also equipped with Adjustable Pedals, Driver Memory, Rear Air/Heat, Power Seats, Power Options and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Power the Tahoe is a 5.3-liter V8 with 320 horsepower and 340 pound-feet of torque. Equipped with GM\'s cylinder deactivation technology, this V8 earns a 15 mpg city/21 mpg highway EPA rating. A four-speed automatic transmission is standard. Maximum towing capacity is 7,700 lbs.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','Chevy','Tahoe LT 4x4','18900.00','104435','SUV','Burgundy','Gray Leather','5.3L V8','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Flex-Fuel E85','Bose AM/FM CD','4','07TAHOELT9569','1GNFK13007J119569'),(3515,3515,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Crew Cab, DVD, Navigation, Back Up Camera, Heated/Cooled Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**DVD** **CREW CAB ROOM** **NAVIGATION** **BACK UP CAMERA**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2009 Cadillac Escalade EXT\'s distinctive styling, versatility and gobs of V8 power keep it atop the dwindling list of luxurious pickups. The Escalade EXT offers Potent and smooth powertrain, luxurious ride, attractive interior, versatile midgate design feature.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Escalade EXT owes this split personality to its innovative \"midgate\" design. In normal operation, the midgate serves as the cabin\'s rear wall, separating the plush five-passenger interior from the truck bed. When more cargo room is needed, the midgate can be lowered and the rear seats stowed, allowing the 5-foot-long truck bed to extend 3 more feet into the cabin.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2009 Cadillac Escalade EXT is a premium full-size crew cab pickup truck. Equipment includes xenon headlights, a roof rack, a road-sensing adaptive suspension, a fold-down midgate, heated/cooled seats, power-adjustable front seats with driver memory settings, leather upholstery, wood grain trim, dual-zone automatic climate control, remote engine start and hands-free Bluetooth via OnStar. Also standard are a navigation system with real-time traffic and an eight-speaker Bose surround-sound audio system with a CD/DVD/MP3 player and satellite radio.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Escalade EXT is a potent 6.2-liter V8 producing 403 horsepower and 417 pound-feet of torque. Power is fed through a six-speed automatic transmission with a tow/haul mode.