ion, Back Up Camera, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**DVD** **NAVIGATION** **BACK UP CAMERA** **8 PASSENGER**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2007 GMC Yukon Denali AWD V8 continues as a leading choice for a traditional large SUV with **3rd Row Seating** thanks to its handsome styling, comfortable cabin and strong towing and hauling capabilities. The Yukon Denali offers High-quality fit and finish, a handsome cabin, comfortable ride, smooth powertrain, seats up to seven passengers.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Yukon Denali also features a unique grille and trim, 18-inch alloy wheels, running boards, adaptive suspension with rear load-leveling, heated and cooled seats, a power-adjustable and heated steering wheel, triple-zone automatic climate control, power-adjustable pedals, rear power lift gate, remote vehicle starter, rear parking assist, universal home remote, a six-disc CD changer with premium Bose sound and \"Turn-by-Turn\" navigation for the OnStar system.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The GMC Yukon Denali features a 6.2-liter V8 that makes 403 hp and 417 lb-ft of torque, mated to a six-speed automatic transmission with tap-up/tap-down shifting. A properly equipped Yukon can tow from 8,200 to 8,500 pounds depending on model and engine specs. Fuel Economy is 12 MPG City and 18 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Antilock disc brakes, stability control, OnStar communications, front-seat side impact airbags and full-length head curtain airbags with rollover sensor are standard on all Yukons.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','GMC','Yukon Denali AWD V8 with 3rd Row Seating','21900.00','108979','SUV','Black','Black Leather','6.2L V8','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','AWD','Gas','Bose AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','07YUKONDENALI5741','1GKFK638X7J295741'),(3810,3810,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>62K Miles, 4 Cylinder Gas Saver</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**62K MILES** With the 2007 Pontiac G6 Sedan, GM\'s performance division offers an enticing entry in the midsize sedan market thanks to distinctive features, sharp styling, a roomy interior and solid performance.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This G6 is equipped with Cloth Interior and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the G6 is a 2.4-liter four-cylinder with 169 hp and 162 pound-feet of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 20 MPG City and 30 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','Pontiac','G6 4 Cylinder','6995.00','62866','4 Door','Blue','Gray Cloth','2.4L 4 Cylinder','4 Speed Automatic','Front Wheel Drive','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','07G6SEDAN7453','1G2ZF58BX74197453'),(3811,3811,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>4x4, 5.3L V8, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powerful and comfortable, The 2008 GMC Sierra 1500 SLE Ext Cab 4x4 Short Bed is a prime choice for a full-size pickup. The Sierra offers a Refined and very quiet ride, pleasing fit and finish inside, the seats are comfortable for long drives, and a comprehensive list of safety equipment.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Sierra is equipped with Cloth Interior, Power Seats, Power Options, Soft Top Tonneau Cover, Bed Liner and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering this Sierra is a 5.3-liter V8 which pumps out 315 hp and 338 lb-ft pound of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 14 MPG City and 18 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','GMC','Sierra 1500 SLE Ext Cab 4x4 Short Bed','17495.00','110311','Pickup','Black','Gray Cloth','5.3L V8','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','08SIERRA1500SLE3389','2GTEK190281113389'),(3692,3692,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>3rd Row, AWD, V6</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>With its stylish good looks, spacious cabin, carlike ride and handling, plus decent fuel economy, the 2011 Chevrolet Traverse LS AWD with **3rd Row Seating** has much to offer SUV owners looking to downsize. The Traverse offers Compliant ride; seating for up to eight passengers; adult-friendly, split-folding third-row seat; massive cargo area; top safety scores.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard equipment on the LS includes 17-inch steel wheels, eight-passenger seating, split-folding second- and third-row bench seats, a tilt-and-telescoping steering wheel, air-conditioning, full power accessories, OnStar and a six-speaker CD/MP3 player with an auxiliary audio jack and satellite radio.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Traverse is a 3.6-liter V6 mated to a six-speed automatic with manual shift control. This V6 produces 281 horsepower and 266 pound-feet of torque. EPA fuel economy estimates for the AWD Traverse are 16 mpg city/23 mpg highway and 19 mpg combined. Properly equipped, the Traverse can tow up to 5,200 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Antilock disc brakes, traction and stability control, front seat side-impact airbags and side curtain airbags for all three rows are all standard on the 2011 Chevrolet Traverse. In the government\'s new, more strenuous crash testing for 2011, the Traverse earned a top five-star rating for overall performance, with four out of five stars being given for front-impact protection and five stars for side-impact protection. The Traverse also aced the Insurance Institute for Highway Safety crash tests, where it got the highest rating of \"Good\" in both the frontal-offset and side-impact tests.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2011','Chevy','Traverse LS AWD','12900.00','126006','SUV','Blue','Gray Cloth','3.6L V6','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','AWD','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','11TRAVERSELS0977','1GNKVFED1BJ310977'),(3548,3548,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>AWD, 4 Cylinder, 25 MPG&nbsp;</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Practical, well-built and enjoyable to drive, the Forester offers an excellent balance of upscale features and all-weather drivability.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Forester is equipped with Cloth Interior and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Forester is a 2.5L 4 Cylinder Engine that gets Fuel Economy of 19 MPG City and 25 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2004','Subaru','Forester 2.5X AWD','7900.00','134660','SUV','Burgundy','Tan Cloth','2.5L 4 Cylinder','4 Speed Automatic','AWD','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','04FORESTER3572','JF1SG63624H703572'),(3603,3603,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Navigation, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**NAVIGATION** **HEATED LEATHER** **POWER SUNROOF** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>In true Jeep form, the 2009 Liberty Limited 4x4 V6 remains a champ off-road, features a simple and functional cabin, high towing capacity, decent luggage space, and a brawny image.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Liberty is equipped with uconnect hard-drive-based navigation system, which includes real-time traffic, digital music storage, a USB audio jack and Bluetooth, Power Seats, Driver Memory, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Liberty is powered by a 3.7-liter V6 that produces 210 horsepower and 235 pound-feet of torque. A four-speed automatic is standard. Fuel Economy clocks in at 15 MPG City and 21 MPG Hwy. Properly equipped, the Liberty can tow up to 5,000 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Antilock disc brakes, stability control, traction control, electronic roll mitigation and side curtain airbags are all standard on the 2009 Jeep Liberty. The National Highway Traffic Safety Administration awarded the Liberty a perfect five-star rating in both front and side impact crashworthiness.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2009','Jeep','Liberty Limited 4x4 V6','12900.00','125708','SUV','Blue','Black Leather','3.7L V6','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','09LIBERTY0522','1J8GN58K29W540522'),(3819,3819,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Power Folding 3rd Row, V8, Heated Leather, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**Power Folding 3rd Row** **Heated Leather** **V8 Power** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The midsize 2007 Ford Explorer Eddie Bauer 4x4 V8 deserves consideration from anyone shopping for a traditional SUV, thanks to its superb road manners, long list of safety features and usable seating in all three rows. The Explorer features Excellent ride and handling characteristics for a truck-based SUV, spacious and quiet interior with user-friendly layout, standard stability control system and integrated rollover sensor.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Eddie Bauer models provide two-tone paint, 17-inch alloy wheels, running boards, leather upholstery, a power adjustable driver seat, heated front seats, faux wood interior trim and an auto-dimming rearview mirror as well as adjustable pedals, driver memory, rear air/heat, power options and 6 disc cd changer with Aux port.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering this Explorer is a 4.6-liter V8 engine with 292 hp and 300 lb-ft of torque. Properly equipped the Explorer can Tow up to 7300 Pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>All major safety equipment is standard on the 2007 Ford Explorer, including four-wheel antilock disc brakes, a stability control system, front seat-mounted side airbags, first- and second-row side curtain airbags optional on the XLT and a tire-pressure monitoring system. The stability control system includes an important feature called Roll Stability Control RSC, which uses a gyro sensor to calculate the SUV\'s roll speed and angle. If RSC determines a rollover is imminent, it activates the regular stability control to help avoid it. The Ford Explorer earned a perfect five stars in all frontal- and side-impact crash tests conducted by the NHTSA, as well as the top rating of \"Good\" in IIHS\' frontal-offset crash testing.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','Ford','Explorer Eddie Bauer 4x4 V8','9900.00','134022','SUV','Black','Tan Leather','4.6L V8','6 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','07EXPLOREREB4049','1FMEU74827UB84049'),(3454,3454,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, 4x4, V6, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>A strong drivetrain, plenty of room inside and a long features list make the 2005 Chevy Trailblazer LS 4X4 an attractive family vehicle. The Trailblazer features Strong engine performance, comfortable highway ride, extensive features list, and user-friendly controls.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Trailblazer is equipped with Cloth Interior, Power Drivers Seat, Power Options, Rear Heat/Air, and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Trailblazer is a 4.2L I-6 Cylinder Engine that gets Fuel Economy of 14 MPG City and 19 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2005','Chevy','Trailblazer LS 4x4','7995.00','116970','SUV','Charcoal','Gray Cloth','4.2L 6 Cylinder','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','05TRLBLZR7652','1GNDT13S152257652'),(2478,2478,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, Heated/Cooled Leather Seats, Power Sunroof</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**One Owner** The 2010 Lexus ES 350 remains a top choice among entry-level luxury sedans. The ES 350 boasts Powerful and velvety-smooth V6, plush ride, sumptuous interior, and high-end luxury features.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The cabin is stocked with high-quality materials that are screwed together to a degree befitting the reputation Lexus has achieved over the years the Camry can\'t make the same claim. Ambient noise is quelled to a level that may make you question your hearing, while the isolated ride melts road imperfections away. The V6 engine is civilized and offers a pleasing mix of power and fuel economy. In short, the ES 350 is designed to comfortably whisk you away from that long day at the office while drawing as little attention to itself as possible.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>For 2010, the ES 350 gets a mild exterior freshening and a significant bolstering of its features list. Now standard are rear side airbags, leather upholstery, driver memory functions, Bluetooth audio and a USB port.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard equipment on the ES 350 includes 17-inch alloy wheels, heated and ventilated front seats, a sunroof, automatic wipers, cruise control, keyless ignition/entry, dual-zone automatic climate control, 10-way power front seats, driver memory functions, a power tilt-and-telescoping steering column, leather upholstery, auto-dimming mirror, Bluetooth phone and music streaming capability, and an eight-speaker stereo with in-dash six-CD changer, satellite radio, iPod interface, auxiliary audio jack and USB audio jack.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2010 Lexus ES 350 is powered by a 3.5-liter V6 that doles out a silky smooth 272 horsepower and 254 pound-feet of torque. Front-wheel drive and a six-speed automatic transmission are standard. Estimated fuel economy stands at 19 mpg city/27 mpg highway and 22 mpg combined.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2010','Lexus','ES 350','23900.00','72375','4 Door','Black','Beige Leather','3.5L V6','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','Front Wheel Drive','Gas','AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','363811','JTHBK1EG4A2363811'),(2951,2951,'<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 0); font-size: large;\"><strong>One Owner, Automatic, Hard Top, 4x4, V6</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**One Owner** The highly sought after 2011 Jeep Wrangler Unlimited Sport 4x4 with Auto Transmission remains a no-nonsense Off Road American icon. The Wrangler boasts Superior off-road capability, is surprisingly fun to drive around town, has a rough-and-tumble image, 4 doors for passenger fun, and has a removable Hard Top. The Jeep Wrangler receives a new interior for 2011, with improved materials, increased acoustic insulation, larger rear windows and new available features.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Wrangler comes standard with foglamps, tow package, power windows and locks, cruise control, height-adjustable driver seat, tilt-only steering wheel, a one-piece flip-and-fold removable rear seat and a six-speaker sound system with a CD player, an auxiliary audio jack and steering wheel controls. The Unlimited Sport gets air-conditioning, a 60/40-split-folding rear seat and a bigger fuel tank.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Jeep Wrangler is powered by a 3.8-liter V6 that produces 202 horsepower and 237 pound-feet of torque. EPA-estimated fuel economy is 15 mpg city/19 mpg highway and 17 mpg combined.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>All 2011 Jeep Wranglers feature antilock brakes, stability control and hill start assist.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Sold','2011','Jeep','Wrangler Unlimited Sport 4x4','24995.00','98217','SUV','Silver','Gray Cloth','3.8L V6','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','597964','1J4BA3H18BL597964'),(3759,3759,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>DVD, 3rd row, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**DVD** **3RD ROW SEATING** **HEATED LEATHER** **POWER SUNROOF**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>With its pleasant ride, comfortable seating in all three rows and spacious cargo hold, the 2008 Saturn Outlook XR AWD offers a mix of comfort and versatility rarely found in SUVs. The Outlook features Smooth ride, easy access to all seats, plenty of room for people or cargo.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>standard features like 18-inch wheels, full power accessories, heated exterior mirrors, cruise control, air-conditioning with rear controls, GM\'s OnStar service, an MP3-compatible CD player and satellite radio. The XR adds roof rails, foglights, variable-effort power steering, a power driver seat, a leather-wrapped steering wheel with remote audio controls, wood-grain interior trim, dual-zone climate control, an auto-dimming rearview mirror, a trip computer and a garage door opener.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Outlook is a 3.6-liter V6 rated at 275 hp and 251 pound-feet of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 16 MPG City and 22 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard safety features include antilock brakes, rollover-sensing stability control, front-seat side airbags, full-length side-curtain airbags and GM\'s OnStar service. In crash tests, the 2008 Saturn Outlook scored an optimal five out of five stars in both front- and side-impact evaluations conducted by the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','Saturn','Outlook XR AWD','12995.00','119443','SUV','Black','Black Leather','3.6L V6','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','AWD','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','08OUTLOOKXR2580','5GZEV23728J172580'),(3604,3604,'<p><span style=\"fo