o schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2006','Volkswagen','Jetta TDI with PKG 1','9995.00','142019','4 Door','Gray','Gray Leather','1.9L 4 Cylinder Diesel','6 Speed Automatic','Front Wheel Drive','Diesel','AM/FM CD','4','759834','3VWST71K16M759834'),(3761,3761,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, 3rd Row, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** **3RD ROW SEATING** **HEATED LEATHER** **POWER SUNROOF WITH SKYLIGHTS**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2009 Ford Flex SEL AWD with **3rd Row Seating** is a thoughtfully designed and cool-looking alternative to minivans and seven-passenger crossover SUVs. This Flex offers Genuine seven-passenger accommodations, high-quality interior materials, unique styling, all-wheel drive, and availability of Sync multimedia interface.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Flex is equipped with Heated Leather, Power Seats, Rear Climate Control, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Flex is a 3.5-liter V6 that churns out 262 horsepower and 248 pound-feet of torque. A six-speed automatic transmission is standard. Fuel Economy clocks in at 16 MPG City and 23 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard safety features on the 2009 Ford Flex include antilock brakes, stability control, front-seat side airbags and full-length side curtain airbags.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available f