ered by the same 5.4-liter V8 that drives other Ford trucks. It\'s good for 300 horsepower and 365 pound-feet of torque, and sends its power through a six-speed automatic transmission. Fuel Economy clocks in at 12 MPG City and 17 MPG Hwy. Properly equipped, the Navigator\'s towing capacity is 9,100 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Lincoln offers a comprehensive list of standard safety features for its flagship SUV including stability control with a rollover sensor, antilock disc brakes with brake assist, traction control, tire-pressure monitoring and power adjustable pedals. Airbag coverage includes seat-mounted side airbags for front occupants and three-row side curtain airbags. In federal government NHTSA crash tests, the 2007 Lincoln Navigator received five out of five stars for its protection of front occupants in head-on</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','Lincoln','Navigator Ultimate Edition 4x4 with 3rd Row Seating','17900.00','122308','SUV','Pearl','Gray Leather','5.4L V8','6 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','07NAVIGATOR2630','5LMFU28507LJ22630'),(3698,3698,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, 7.3L Diesel, 8 Passenger, VCR Entertainment, Heated Leather, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** &nbsp;**7.3L V8 POWER STROKE DIESEL** **HEATED LEATHER** **8 PASSENGER** **VCR ENTERTAINMENT** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>A very rare find in this clean and sharp 2001 Ford Excursion Limited 4x4 that sports the much sought after and rare to find 7.3L Disel Engine. 