lering package. Stability control, front side and side curtain airbags are also standard.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2010','Chevy','Silverado 1500 LS Crew Cab 4x4 Short Bed','16900.00','145475','Pickup','Gray','Gray Cloth','4.8L V8','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Flex-Fuel E85','AM/FM CD','4','10SILVERADO1500LS6879','3GCRKREA9AG226879'),(3678,3678,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>DVD, Navigation, Bucket Seats, Back Up Camera, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**DVD** **NAVIGATION** **BUCKET SEATS** **BACK UP CAMERA** **REAR POWER LIFT GATE** **POWER SUNROOF** **HEATED LEATHER**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2008 GMC Yukon XL Denali AWD with 3rd Row Seating is an excellent choice for large families who need a full-size Luxury SUV with maximum seating, towing and cargo capacities. The Yukon XL offers Seating for up to seven passengers, only slightly less interior space than the Astrodome, smooth road manners, and attractive interior with quality materials.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Yukon XL is also equipped with Adjustable Pedals, Driver Memory, Bose Sound, Rear Air/Heat, Power Options and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The GMC Yukon Denali boasts a 6.2-liter V8 380 hp and 415 lb-ft matched to a six-speed automatic transmission with a manual-shift mode. Fuel Economy clocks in at 12 MPG City and 18 MPG Hwy. Properly equipped, a Yukon Denali can tow up to 7900 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Stability control dubbed StabiliTrak with a rollover sensor is standard, as are antilock disc brakes, side curtain airbags and the OnStar telematics system. In government crash tests, the 2008 GMC Yukon XL was awarded five stars for protecting the driver and passenger in a frontal collision.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2008','GMC','Yukon XL Denali AWD','23900.00','113957','SUV','Gold','Tan Leather','6.2L V8','6 Speed Shiftable Automatic','AWD','Gas','Bose AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','08YUKONXLDENALI5337','1GKFK66828J125337'),(3608,3608,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>93K Miles, 4x4, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>A strong drivetrain, plenty of room inside and a long features list make the 2006 Chevrolet Trailblazer LT 4x4 with **Power Sunroof** an attractive family vehicle for those looking for a mid sized 4x4 with 6 Cylinder Gas Mileage. The Trailblazer features Strong engine performance, comfortable highway ride, extensive features list, and user-friendly controls.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>LT models come equipped with such features as 16-inch aluminum wheels, cloth interior, dual-zone manual air conditioning, cruise control, OnStar, a CD player and power windows and locks and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The TrailBlazer\'s standard 4.2-liter inline six puts out 291 horsepower and 277 lb-ft of torque. Fuel Economy clocks in at 14 MPG City and 20 MPG Hwy. Properly equipped the Trailblazer can Tow up to 6200 Pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"tex