e stars for frontal collision protection, and a perfect five stars for side protection. In Insurance Institute for Highway Safety crash tests, the Jetta sedan received the highest rating of \"Good\" for frontal offset and side crash protection.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2009','Volkswagen','Jetta TDI','12495.00','131642','4 Door','Gray','Gray Leather','2.0L 4 Cylinder Turbo Diesel','DSG Automatic','Front Wheel Drive','Diesel','AM/FM CD','4','138125','3VWRL71K89M138125'),(3583,3583,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>DVD, 8 Passenger, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**DVD** **POWER SUNROOF** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2007 Chevrolet Suburban LT 4x4 is completely redesigned. Interior materials quality is dramatically improved, and the Suburban now has cleaner exterior styling, more accurate steering and a bit more power. If you need a full-size SUV with maximum capacity, the Suburban is a compelling choice. The Suburban boasts an attractive interior with solid materials, comfortable ride and seating, smooth V8, accommodates up to eigh passengers, and has class-leading cargo capacity.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Suburban is equipped with Heated Leather Interior, Adjustable Pedals, Traction Control, Rear Heat/Air, Rear Power Lift Gate, Power Options and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Suburban is powered by a 5.3-liter V8 with 320 horsepower and 340 pound-feet of torque. Equipped with GM\'s cylinder deactivation technology, this V8 promises improved fuel-efficiency over last year\'s engine. Towing capacity is 8,000 pounds. Fuel Economy clocks in at 14 MPG City and 19 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Four-wheel antilock disc brakes are standard on all Suburbans, as is stability control, a tire-pressure monitoring system and GM\'s OnStar emergency communications system.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','Chevy','Suburban LT 4x4 with 3rd Row Seating','17900.00','135785','SUV','Silver Birch Metallic','Black Leather','5.3L V8','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','07SUBURBANLT2331','3GNFK16347G102331'),(3768,3768,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>DVD, Bucket Seats, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**DVD** **BUCKET SEATS** **HEATED LEATHER** **POWER SUNROOF** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The GMC Yukon XL SLT 4x4 bridges the gap between the somewhat plain Chevy Suburban and the over-the-top Cadillac Escalade ESV. The Yukon XL is essentially a longer version of the Yukon, with a 14-inch-longer wheelbase and an overall length that, at 222.4 inches, stretches some 20 inches longer than the Yukon. The 2007 GMC Yukon XL is completely redesigned and gets more of everything that\'s important in the large SUV segment power, cabin space, convenience features and safety equipment.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Yukon XL comes equipped with 17-inch alloy wheels, power windows, adjustable pedals, locks and mirrors, keyless entry, a front split bench seat with six-way power driver seat, triple-zone climate control, rear power lift gate, a trip computer, heated leather seating, a six-disc Bose CD changer, power adjustable pedals, remote vehicle starting and rear parking assist.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Yukon XL is a 5.3-liter V8 making 320 horsepower and 340 pound-feet of torque. Equipped with GM\'s cylinder deactivation technology, this V8 provides slightly improved fuel economy over last year\'s engine. Towing capacity for the Yukon XL is 7,100 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Stability control dubbed StabiliTrak with a rollover sensor is standard, as are four-wheel antilock disc brakes, a tire-pressure monitoring system and the OnStar telematics system. Standard on the Yukon XL SLT are head curtain airbags for all three rows.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','GMC','Yukon XL SLT 4x4','18495.00','119057','SUV','Burgundy','Gray Leather','5.3L V8','4 Speed Automatic','4x4','Flex-Fuel E85','Bose AM/FM CD','4','07YUKONXL3527','1GKFK16327J303527'),(3122,3122,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>4x4, V6</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2004 Jeep Liberty is a thoroughly capable and comfortable compact SUV that is Extremely capable off-road, has creative interior design, and is still a Jeep at heart.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Liberty is equipped with Cloth Interior, Shiftable 4x4, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-