tection.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2009','Lincoln','MKX AWD','13495.00','126403','SUV','White','Tan Leather','3.5L V6','6 Speed Automatic','AWD','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','09MKXAWD9449','2LMDU88CX9BJ09449'),(3258,3258,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>4 Cylinder Gas Saver, Sharp</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The 2009 Chevy Cobalt LT is a solid compact 4 Door Sedan with a Fuel Efficient 4 Cylinder Gas Saving engine. A great choice for someone looking for a clean, nice running compact 4 door car.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Cobalt is equipped with Cloth Interior, A/C, Power Options and CD Player.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Cobalt is a 2.2L 4 Cylinder Engine that gets Fuel Economy of 22 MPG City and 32 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2009','Chevy','Cobalt LT','7495.00','95601','4 Door','Black','Gray Cloth','2.2L 4 Cylinder','4 Speed Automatic','Front Wheel Drive','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','09COBALT0685','1G1AT58H397290685'),(3702,3702,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Crew Cab, Heated Leather, Power Sunroof, Tow Package</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**CREW CAB ROOM** **HEATED LEATHER** **POWER SUNROOF** **TOW PACKAGE**</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Boasting a refined cabin along with a comfortable ride and strong workhorse capabilities, the 2007 GMC Sierra 1500 SLT Z71 Crew Cab 4x4 Short Bed stands as a major contender for top honors in the full-siz