an></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Ram Sport is equipped with Leather Wrapped Cloth Interior, Power Drivers Seat, Dual Climate Control, Power Options, and Tow Package.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering this Ram is a a 5.7-liter V8 with a five-speed auto. Output is 390 hp and 407 lb-ft of torque. Fuel Economy is 13 MPG City and 19 MPG Hwy. Maximum towing capacity when properly equipped is 10,250 pounds.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard safety equipment on the 2010 Dodge Ram 1500 includes four-wheel antilock disc brakes, stability control, hill-start assist, trailer-sway control, front-seat side airbags and full-length side curtain airbags. In government crash tests, the Ram was awarded the highest score of five out of five stars for frontal and side-impact protection for all passengers. The Insurance Institute for Highway Safety also gave the Ram its highest score of \"Good\" for frontal-offset crash protection.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2010','Dodge','Ram 1500 Sport Crew Cab 4x4 Short Bed Hemi V8','26900.00','75145','Pickup','Burnt Orange','Gray Cloth','5.7L Hemi V8','5 Speed Shiftable Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','10RAM1500SPORT4561','1D7RV1CT6AS204561'),(3732,3732,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, Clean, V6</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** Take a look at this clean and solid running 2005 Ford Taurus SE. A great choice for a family looking for an inexpensive sedan or a car for a student driver.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Taurus is equipped with Cloth Interior, Air, Cruise, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Taurus is a 3.0L V6 that gets Fuel Economy of 18 MPG City and 25 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2005','Ford','Taurus SE','4995.00','113710','4 Door','Tan','Gray Cloth','3.0L V6','4 Speed Automatic with Overdrive','Front Wheel Drive','Gas','AM/FM CD','4','05TAURUSSE2342','1FAFP53U85A262342'),(3738,3738,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>One Owner, 4x4, 4 Cylinder</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**ONE OWNER** The 2007 Jeep Compass is a decent compact SUV with Comfortable seats, low price, cool gadgets, and it drives with the agility of a small car.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This Compass is equipped with Cloth Interior, Heated Seats, and Power Options.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>This compass is powered by a 2.4-liter 4-cylinder engine capable of 172 horsepower and 165 pound-feet of torque. Four-wheel-drive models operate in front-wheel drive in normal situations and automatically and seamlessly apply power to the rear wheels when needed. The system can also be locked with up to 60 percent of the engine\'s torque supplied to the rear wheels for better off-road traction. Fuel Economy clocks in at 21 MPG City and 26 MPG Hwy.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard safety features include stability control with a rollover sensor, full-length side curtain airbags and traction control. Front seat-mounted side airbags are optional. Limited models have a standard tire-pressure monitoring system.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Give us a call to schedule a test drive or if you have additional questions. Warranty available for purchase.</strong></span></p>',6,'Normal','2007','Jeep','Compass Sport 4x4','8495.00','100492','SUV','Silver','Gray Cloth','2.4L 4 Cylinder','Continuously Variable Automatic','4x4','Gas','AM/FM 6 DISC CD CHANGER','4','07COMPASS7608','1J8FF47W97D167608'),(3739,3739,'<p><span style=\"font-size: large; color: #ffff00;\"><strong>Local Trade, 4 Cylinder</strong></span></p>',6,'<p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>**LOCAL TRADE IN** The 2011 Chevrolet Malibu remains a popular, well-equipped entry in the hotly contested segment of midsize family sedans. The Malibu features economical inline-4; fine ride and handling balance; quiet cabin high scores in crash tests.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Standard equipment on the Malibu LS includes 17-inch steel wheels, automatic headlights, keyless entry, cruise control, air-conditioning, full power accessories, a tilt-and-telescoping steering column, OnStar and a six-speaker stereo with CD player, satellite radio and auxiliary audio jack.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>Powering the Malibu is a 2.4-liter four-cylinder engine which generates 169 horsepower and 160 pound-feet of torque. Power is sent through the front wheels via a six-speed automatic transmission with manual shift control. Estimated fuel economy checks in at 22 mpg city/33 mpg highway and 26 mpg combined.</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><strong>The Chevy Malibu comes standard with antilock 